'''Gary M. Sarli''' is an author, game designer, developer, and editor who wrote [[Jedi Counseling]] from [[2004]] to [[2010]], a regular feature on the [[Wizards of the Coast]] website that provided rules clarifications for players of the [[Star Wars Roleplaying Game]] and [[Star Wars Miniatures]]. He also worked as the editor and developer for the ''[[Star Wars Roleplaying Game Saga Edition Core Rulebook]]'' as well as several other supplements and features for the Star Wars Roleplaying Game.

